    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the kidney beans are beginning to break down, season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and squeeze in the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Remove the beans from the heat and mash into a semi-smooth paste – these are your <strong>refried beans</strong></p>",
