            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> quesadillas </strong>to a baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Place a second baking tray[s] on top to weigh them down slightly</p><p>Put the stacked trays<strong> </strong>in the oven for 10 min or until the quesadillas are slightly browned and the cheese has melted – these are your <strong>refried bean & corn quesadillas</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
