            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lime</strong> with 2 tbsp [3 tbsp] [4 tbsp] <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>salad dressing</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>mayo</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>refried bean & corn quesadillas</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and dress it with the <strong>salad dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
