    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>refried bean & corn quesadillas</strong> alongside the <strong>dressed</strong> <strong>salad</strong> and the<strong> chipotle mayo</strong> for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
